 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">can be seen at the horizon is too easily ridiculed by cynics or the media</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> so studies </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">tend to be</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">launched somewhat later and are </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">thus </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">on issues that have already </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">appeared</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">over the horizon</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> and</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 72pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-32.4pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">(c)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">successful </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">adoption and utilisation of</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> a study </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">depends</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">on the extent to which the work was locked in to internal strategic thinking and option analysis and also the degree to which there was a political involvement either directly or </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; fo